19 August 2010Members of the media are invited to a media briefing of the Justice, Crime Prevention and Security cluster. The briefing follows a meeting of ministers in the cluster to discuss a coordinated approach to security during the public service strike.The briefing will take place as follows:-Date: Friday, 20 August 2010 Time: 11h30 Venue: State Security Agency Ministry, Bogare Building, Corner Atterbury and Lois Avenue, Menlyn, PretoriaRSVP with:David Masango 083 279 7520For media enquiries contact:Brian Dube 082 418 3389Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)